            <p><font size="4"><b>Crossover – Now only $349</b></font></p>
<iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/DspQZsK3nek" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

<p></p>

<p><strong>Tippmann Crossover .68 Caliber Paintball Marker</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>FlexValve Technology allows operation under 300PSI, reduces recoil and improves air efficiency</li>
<li>Three position selector switch changes from electronic to mechanical operation on the fly</li>
<li>Center feed system</li>
<li>Break-beam anti-chop eye system</li>
<li>Magnetically activated Hall-Effect Electronics provides 6 firing modes including Safety Full-auto, 3-Shot Burst, NPPL, PSP, Millennium, Auto-Response or Semi-Auto</li>
</ul>
<p>The Crossover is a lightweight, high performance tournament-style paintball marker designed to handle the rigors of woodsball or any style of play. The Crossover features low pressure operation, aluminum receiver, internal gas line, clamping feedneck, 12” high performance barrel, double finger blade trigger, bottom regulator with ability to convert to a front regulator and, of course, Tippmann’s World Class 2-year Warranty.</p>
